    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，命名没问题。第一条确实是 Update records，这是同步调用。然后 Network/DNS 处理完之后，需要异步回调通知 propagation 完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Update records",
        "Propagation complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画一下：Migrate Tooling 到 Network/DNS 的实线箭头标 Update records，然后 Network/DNS 返回虚线箭头标 Propagation complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Migrate Tooling",
        "Network/DNS",
        "Update records",
        "Propagation complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，回调箭头的方向反了。应该是 Network/DNS 指向 Migrate Tooling，不是 Migrate Tooling 指回去。而且 propagation complete 是异步通知，用虚线是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Network/DNS",
        "Migrate Tooling",
        "Propagation complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在 Network/DNS 用虚线箭头指向 Migrate Tooling，标注 Propagation complete。整个时序是：M→N 实线 Update records，然后 N--M 虚线 Propagation complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Migrate Tooling",
        "Network/DNS",
        "Update records",
        "Propagation complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
